It&#39;s almost precisely the same reason I feel Kennedy is an idiot cuz he took a similar stance during the Cuban Missile Crisis and basically just dared them (soviets) to take it to the next level. Consequences would have been dire. <br><BR><font size=1>08:19 02-26-2011</font></TD></TR><TR><td width='4' bgcolor=#FFFFFF>&nbsp;</td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont"><B>Darth Bear </B></font><br><font class="afont"> <A HREF='/vs/resources/buzz.php?ignorename=Darth Bear '>Ignore</A></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor='#FFFFFF' ><font class="bfont">And to fill in some of facts that I&#39;m sure Neal just missed when recounting this story.<br />
<br />
<blockquote><i>In the early 1980s, Reagan was, as usual, looking for a fight with someone.</i></blockquote><br />
<br />
As usual?  Explain this.  Where else was he looking for a fight?<br />
<br />
<blockquote><i>He tells Reagan, look stay out of that gulf, it&#39;s ours. Reagan tells him to piss off, it&#39;s "international" and puts navy ships there.</i></blockquote><br />
<br />
Reagan was absolutely correct here and the international community agreed with him.  This might have even passed John Kerry&#39;s international "test".<br />
<br />
<blockquote><i>Ghaddafi is furious, and sends some planes out, which promptly get shot down.</i></blockquote><br />
<br />
...after they fired first on American aircraft.<br />
<br />
<blockquote><i>Then the us navy sinks a few Libyan ships, just to show who is boss.</i></blockquote><br />
<br />
Libya sent the patrol boats towards the US fleet.  Should we have just left them alone?  Would it have been better to have a US Cole incident instead?<br />
<br />
<blockquote><i>Reagan, to get even, bombs the guy&#39;s frimbazelING HOUSE, and kills a bunch of his close friends and allies including his DAUGHTER for christ&#39;s sake.</i></blockquote><br />
<br />
So what would have been a better response?  Nothing?  Yeah that worked real well against Bin Laden.  Perhaps we should have done some indiscriminate carpet bombing in Triploli.  Yeah, I&#39;m sure you think that would have been a much better response.  No, this was probably the best way to respond to the incident...only against the one who organized the bombing.  The loss of Ghaddafi&#39;s daughter was tragic, but perhaps the terrorism business isn&#39;t all its cracked up to be.<br />
<br />
<blockquote><i>Instead they use sanctions, which as always, are very effective.</i></blockquote><br />
<br />
Always effective at what?  Hurting the people of the country who is being sanctioned?  I certainly didn&#39;t see people like Ghaddaffi, Hussein of Kim Jon Ill affected by sanctions.  There certainly didn&#39;t miss any meals.  The people, however, were greatly affected.<br />
<br />
<blockquote><i>And all of this is because that stupid macho frimbazeling fool Reagan wanted to start a fight. He is no different then Ghaddafi if you ask me.</i></blockquote><br />
<br />
And the lesson, as always, is to back down to the demands of terrorists. <br><BR><font size=1>08:18 02-26-2011</font></TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#C3E3FF><img src='/global/images/premium_icon.gif' border='0' hspace='1' vspace='1'></td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#C3E3FF><font class="bfont"><B><a href="http://www.decktech.net/magic/main/mpage.php?member=17">Dredlox™</a></B></font><br><font class="afont"> <A HREF='/vs/resources/buzz.php?ignorename=<a href="http://www.decktech.net/magic/main/mpage.php?member=17">Dredlox™</a>'>Ignore</A></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor='#C3E3FF' ><font class="bfont">Booth, isn&#39;t there some screwball 50s sci fi where Reagan is firing lasers at aliens?  Is that where you got that name? <br><BR><font size=1>21:22 02-25-2011</font><BR><BR><img src=http://www.takepart.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/80x80/logos/220354-defenders_of_wildlife_o.jpg></TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><img src='/global/images/premium_icon.gif' border='0' hspace='1' vspace='1'></td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont"><B><a href="http://www.decktech.net/magic/main/mpage.php?member=17">Dredlox™</a></B></font><br><font class="afont"> <A HREF='/vs/resources/buzz.php?ignorename=<a href="http://www.decktech.net/magic/main/mpage.php?member=17">Dredlox™</a>'>Ignore</A></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor='#FFFFFF' ><font class="bfont">I think now that his career is done I&#39;d put W above both Reagan (obviously) and his dad. <br><BR><font size=1>21:21 02-25-2011</font><BR><BR><img src=http://www.takepart.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/80x80/logos/220354-defenders_of_wildlife_o.jpg></TD></TR><TR><td width='4' bgcolor=#C3E3FF>&nbsp;</td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#C3E3FF><font class="bfont"><B>boothwah </B></font><br><font class="afont"> <A HREF='/vs/resources/buzz.php?ignorename=boothwah '>Ignore</A></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcol