nt></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor='#FFFFFF' ><font class="bfont">well, the fristing made me laugh, I think it&#39;s the first smile I had all day. Now I better blow my nose for the 300th time. <br><BR><font size=1>19:22 02-25-2011</font><BR><BR><img src=http://www.takepart.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/80x80/logos/220354-defenders_of_wildlife_o.jpg></TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#C3E3FF><img src='/global/images/premium_icon.gif' border='0' hspace='1' vspace='1'></td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#C3E3FF><font class="bfont"><B><a href="http://www.decktech.net/magic/main/mpage.php?member=17">Dredlox™</a></B></font><br><font class="afont"> <A HREF='/vs/resources/buzz.php?ignorename=<a href="http://www.decktech.net/magic/main/mpage.php?member=17">Dredlox™</a>'>Ignore</A></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor='#C3E3FF' ><font class="bfont">Well, I am sick and feel absolutely horrible. This has put me in a very bad mood, so against my better judgement I&#39;m going to give a story that&#39;s typically under the radar from my youth, and you can get an idea of why I say Reagan was the worst president in my lifetime.  <br />
<br />
I know this is going to be a rant, but I&#39;d ask anyone who thinks Reagan was a good leader to read it.<br />
<br />
This is all from my recollection, so I went to Wiki and it all basically was as I remember.  It&#39;s so stupid and insane, I had to be sure I was right.<br />
<br />
This story all starts with Sarah asking me about Muammar Ghadaffi... how did I know so much about him?<br />
<br />
In the early 1980s, Reagan was, as usual, looking for a fight with someone.  So he sends warships into the gulf of Sidra, basically just to get a reaction out of this guy who has lots of oil, but doesn&#39;t like America.<br />
<br />
Now, you might have noticed by what&#39;s happening, Ghaddafi is not the type to back down. From anybody.  He tells Reagan, look stay out of that gulf, it&#39;s ours.  Reagan tells him to piss off, it&#39;s "international" and puts navy ships there.<br />
<br />
Ghaddafi is furious, and sends some planes out, which promptly get shot down. Then the us navy sinks a few Libyan ships, just to show who is boss. Ghaddafi realizes there is no way to fight the US military on their terms, but this is a guy not afraid to keep duking it out. Even if it kills him or anybody.<br />
<br />
So he organizes a bombing of a nightclub in Germany with US soldiers in it, and kills several.  Reagan, to get even, bombs the guy&#39;s frimbazelING HOUSE, and kills a bunch of his close friends and allies including his DAUGHTER for christ&#39;s sake.<br />
<br />
Oh yeah, that&#39;ll learn him, right Reagan? Wrong, dumb ass.  Ghaddafi goes ape shimmer.  He organizes an airline hijacking and bombing, and you dudes haven&#39;t probably heard of it, but it is probably the worst disaster I remember other than 9/11.<br />
<br />
It was this <a href=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lockerbie_bombing> Lockerbie bombing </a>, if you are familiar with it. This pan american jet is flying along, and BOOM, a bomb busts it open.  It just disintegrates and all the people died, 260.  Reputedly half of them were still alive on the way down to die on impact, if you want to read something truly disturbing read the forensic and engineering account of what happened in the explosion.  Horrible, ghastly stuff.<br />
<br />
But that&#39;s not all. No the goddamn plane falls on a bunch of people in Scotland, killing like 10 more, including a family where a kid saw the plane fall on his house.<br />
<br />
Outcome?  Reagan never frimbazels with the guy again. No one does. Instead they use sanctions, which as always, are very effective.  Ghaddafi, a very violent guy, even realizes he&#39;s gone too far, and eventually ends up promising not to do it in exchange for the bombers return to libya and paying a few billion to the families.<br />
<br />
And all of this is because that stupid macho frimbazeling fool Reagan wanted to start a fight.  He is no different then Ghaddafi if you ask me.  I won&#39;t even get into him shooting down a random Iranian airliner for no reason.  The guy was an awful president, dumb as dirt and a truly evil man.<br />
<br />
Thanks for reading, I just had to get that off my chest. <br><BR><font size=1>19:21 02-25-2011</font><BR><BR><img src=http://www.takepart.com/sites/default/files/imagecache/80x80/logos/220354-defenders_of_wildlife_o.jpg></TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><img src='/global/images/premium_icon.gif' border='0' hspace='1' vspace='1'></td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont"><B><a href="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=5142">imrahil327™</a></B></font><br><font class="afont"> <A HREF='/vs/resources/buzz.php?ignorename=<a href="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=5142">imrahil327™</a>'>Ignore</A></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor='#FFFFFF' ><font class="bfont">Thrird of Nine is the bestest Borg. <br><BR><font size=1>19:17 02-25-2011</font><BR><BR><b>Patrick M.S.</b> "ok, I&#39;m going to reinforce Dr Doom with..zzzzzzzzzzzz"</TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#C3E3FF><img src='/global/images/premium_icon.gif' border='0' hspace='1' vspace='1'></td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#C3E3FF><font class="bfont"><B><a href="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=5142">imrahil327™</a></B></font><br><font class="afont"> <A HREF='/vs/resources/buzz.php?ignorename=<a href="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=5142">imrahil327™</a>'>Ignore</A></font></td><Td valign='top' bgcolor='#C3E3FF' ><font class="bfont">/rounds the corner and heads for secrond base. <br><BR><font size=1>19:16 02-25-2011</font><BR><BR><b>Patrick M.S.</b> "ok, I&#39;m going to reinforce Dr Doom with..zzzzzzzzzzzz"</TD></TR><TR><td width='4' valign='top' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><img src='/global/images/premium_icon.gif' border='0' hspace='1' vspace='1'></td><TD ALIGN='LEFT' valign='top' width='70' bgcolor=#FFFFFF><font class="bfont"><B><a href="http://www.decktech.net/lotr/main/mpage.php?member=5142">imrahil327™</a></B></font><br><font class="afont"> <A HREF='/vs/resources